                                            <p style="color:#484848;font-family:'Open Sans',Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;font-weight:normal;padding:0;margin:0;Margin:0;text-align:left;font-size:16px;line-height:1.3;margin-bottom:10px;Margin-bottom:10px">
