                                                En cuanto salga de nuestro almacén te enviaremos un correo para que estés informado del estado del pedido.
                                            </p>
                                            <p style="color:#484848;font-family:'Open Sans',Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;font-weight:normal;padding:0;margin:0;Margin:0;text-align:left;font-size:16px;line-height:1.3;margin-bottom:10px;Margin-bottom:10px">¡Gracias!</p>
                                        <% } %>
                                    </th>
                                </tr>
                                </tbody>
                            </table>
                        </th>
                    </tr>
                    </tbody>
                </table>

                <table style="border-spacing:0;border-collapse:collapse;vertical-align:top;text-align:left;margin-left:0px;padding:0;width:100%;display:table">
                    <tbody>
                    <tr style="padding:0;vertical-align:top;text-align:left">
                        <th style="color:#484848;font-family:'Open Sans',Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;font-weight:normal;padding:0;text-align:left;font-size:16px;line-height:1.3;margin:0 auto;Margin:0 auto;padding-bottom:16px;width:564px;padding-left:16px;padding-right:16px">
                            <table style="border-spacing:0;border-collapse:collapse;padding:0;vertical-align:top;text-align:left;width:100%">
                                <tbody>
                                <tr style="padding:0;vertical-align:top;text-align:left">
                                    <th style="color:#484848;font-family:'Open Sans',Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;font-weight:normal;padding:0;margin:0;Margin:0;text-align:left;font-size:16px;line-height:1.3">
                                        <div style="background-color:#ebebeb; padding: 16px;">
                                            <p style="text-align:center; margin-bottom:16px">Consulta cómo está tu pedido en todo momento.</p>
                                            <center>
                                                <table align="center" style="border-spacing:0;border-collapse:collapse;padding:0;vertical-align:top;float:none;text-align:center;width:auto;margin-bottom:0">
                                                    <tr style="background:#c74044; border-radius:3px">
                                                        <td style="padding:5px 10px">
                                                            <a href="<%= domainHelper.getSiteRoot() %>/Account/OrderDetail.rails?orderId=<%= order.id %>&hash=<%= hash %>" style="color:#fefefe; text-decoration:none; font-weight:bold; font-size:12px" target="_blank">
                                                                Ir al estado del pedido
                                                            </a>
                                                        </td>
                                                    </tr>
                                                </table>
